License: BSD License
Description: # WeChat微信支付
        ------
        ##Overview
        Python-Django WeChat payment API, it contains 4 main classes:
        > * UnifiedOrderPay
        > * NativeOrderPay 
        > * JsAPIOrderPay
        > * OrderQuery
        > * Refund
        > * RefundQuery
        > * DownloadBill
        
        ------
        
        Installation
        ------------
        
        Install using pip:
        
        ```bash
        pip install WeChatPay
        ```
